&lt;p&gt;We are a friendly GP practice in North Chingford, with approx 3800 patients. we are looking for a part-time Practice Nurse to join our team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hours are 22 hours a week, which can be spread over 4 days, with 4 mornings and 2 afternoons a week. We are flexible with this and can consider working with different timetabling.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an applicant that can manage a full range of Practice Nurse Duties: Chronic Disease Management, Experience of QOF, Childhood &amp; Travel Immunisations, cervical smear screening, Dressing &amp; Wound care, Contraception, Health Promotion/ Advice and all other Nurse duties.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;GP Practice knowledge is desirable.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We use Emis web computer system.&lt;/p&gt;
